        <Parent_String>Xiphias (genus) [300310598], Xiphiidae (family) [300310597], Perciformes (order) [300310596], Actinopterygii (subclass) [300310217], Osteichthyes (class) [300265954], Vertebrata (subphylum) [300265720], Chordata (phylum) [300266513], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
